data.description: Beautiful one level, 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home in the nice community of Waterford At Providence! This area is located in the back of the neighborhood. There is a clubhouse with a pool for gatherings with friends, family, or neighbors! Perfect home for a small family or a retired couple looking to downsize. Located just off the Bass Rd Exit on I-75 Interstate. You can't beat the location with being so close to shopping and good food! There is a $360 Monthly HOA Fee that covers the exterior maintenance such as the home itself, roof, yards, lights, etc. along with the pool/clubhouse, and the water/sewage.
